<h3>Payment Information</h3>
<p><strong>Important Security Notice:</strong> We do not directly store or process your complete payment card information on our servers. All payment transactions are processed through secure, PCI-DSS compliant third-party payment processors.</p>

<p>When you make a purchase, your payment information (such as credit card number, expiration date, and CVV) is transmitted directly to our payment processor using industry-standard encryption. We may retain the last four digits of your card number and card type for reference purposes only.</p>

<p>Our payment processors may store your payment information according to their own privacy policies and security standards.</p>
